properties.Name: CostItem
properties.Description:
An item that may be applied to a budget.    Cost Items are usually represented in the chart of accounts and can be applied to more than one budget.

Ex:
- Administration
- Travel & Lodging
- Video production
- Third party contractors
- Utilities 
- Paper
- Computers
- Office Supplies
- Furniture
- Vehicles

Columns.Name: CostItemId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Cost Item.

Columns.Name: CostItemName
Columns.Description: The name of a Cost Item.

Columns.Name: CostItemDescription
Columns.Description: The description of a Cost Item.
